abc=1
1+\frac{3}{a+b+c}\geq \frac{6}{ab+bc+ca}
a=\frac{x}{y}, b=\frac{y}{z}, c=\frac{z}{x}
(ab+bc+ca)^2 \geq 3 (a+b+c)abc 
 (ab-bc)^2 + (bc-ca)^2 + (ca-ab)^2 \geq 0
 1 + \frac{3}{a+b+c} \geq 2 \sqrt{ \frac{3}{a+b+c} } \geq \frac{6}{ab+bc+ca}. 
